We are NYC natives who enjoy using Turo to help you get the cars you want, not just what is left over. Our car fleet is growing and we want you to enjoy them. 

Let's connect, and you'll get a clean car with a full tank for where you want to go.

We at Broadfeet Motorsport are proud to be one of the fast-growing Turo hosts in New York City! ⚡️👏

We have All Star ⭐️ Host and Power 💪🏻 Host status! 

What does this mean for you?

✅ We have more than 540 trips 
✅ No matter what time you want to start or end your reservation we are open 24/7 all year round! 
✅ No need to worry about washing the car before returning it. Regular wash is complimentary. 
✅ All our vehicles normally come with a full tank of gas, so you won't have to deal with the inconvenience of an empty tank.
✅Each Vehicle has an EZPASS Transponder, so you don’t need to worry about it, you pay only your tolls no additional fees. 
✅ I ensure that each car is thoroughly cleaned and washed, so you can enjoy your ride to the fullest.
✅ Delivery ON TIME is our top priority! As soon as we get your booking confirmed you can be certain you will have the car at the needed location right on time! 
✅ We are always here to help, so you can contact us anytime
✅ If you're traveling with kids, you can request car seats for their safety and comfort.

We have cars for all your requests. Please follow the link:

https://turo.com/us/en/drivers/3776395

Welcome to Turo! As a dedicated host, I’m committed to ensuring that every trip you take is not just a drive, but an experience. I take pride in providing meticulously maintained vehicles and a seamless rental process, so you can hit the road with confidence. Book your next adventure with us and discover the joy of the journey!

We are a member-driven car club, dedicated to celebrating the unique character of each vehicle in our collection. Whether you're into exotic sports cars or luxury sedans and SUVs, the MVP Car Collection offers an unmatched variety with personalized service.

Our journey on Turo began with a single car, the 2020 BMW M8, and a singular goal: to curate a selection of our favorite automobiles for your enjoyment at competitive prices. Two years later, that mission remains unchanged.

Today, MVP CarClub proudly boasts a fleet of 14 luxury and exotic cars, and we've earned a reputation as a power host!

Contact us (516)206-2755, visit us at www.mvpcarclub.com and follow us on Instagram: @mvpcarclub

Hi there,

I'm Michael, your Turo host. Welcome to my page! 

My team and I strive to provide a 5 star experience. Our high standards include;

**Safety First:** Your safety is my top priority. Rest assured that every vehicle in our fleet is well-maintained, regularly serviced, and meets all safety standards. Your peace of mind is essential to us.

**Convenience Matters:** We understand that travel plans can be unpredictable. That's why we strive to be flexible and accommodating. Need a last-minute reservation or specific drop-off/pick-up arrangements? Just let us know, and we'll do our best to make it happen.

**Easy Communication:** Open and clear communication is key to a successful Turo experience. You can reach out to us anytime with questions, concerns, or special requests. We’re here to make your trip exceptional.

Feel free to browse our listings and don't hesitate to reach out if you have any questions or specific requirements.

https://turo.com/us/en/drivers/21360764/vehicles

We look forward to hosting you and providing a seamless and enjoyable car rental experience.

Safe travels,
Michael and Team
